<p>We closed the show with our good friend Ellen Barrett. Ellen has a great new exercise dvd for new moms titled Happy Baby Fit Mama. This workout dvd lets you bring your baby along as you exercise and get back in pre-baby shape. Thsi workout dvd is available everywhere but be sure to check out Ellen's website <a href="http://www.ellenbarrett.com">www.ellenbarrett.com</a> to see what she is up to.&nbsp;</p>
