            <description><![CDATA[<p>The most entertaining weight loss and fitness podcast show on radio." Please click on the POD button to listen to the latest&nbsp;<a style="text-decoration: none; color: #4182b8;" href="http://www.drfitnessandthefatguy.com/">Dr. Fitness and the Fat Guy radio show</a>&nbsp;podcast broadcasting live each week from Atlanta, GA, USA.</p>
