Also we would like to welcome back Celeste Katz, The Card Mom, as one of our local sponsors. Celeste will help you <span>send your holiday greeting cards from the comfort </span><span>of your own home. There are over 13,000 designs at thecardmom.com  on-lin</span><span>e card store. Folks, these are NOT e-cards but beautiful, high quality,  gloss</span><span>y greeting cards printed on 100% recycled paper.</span><span> Just select your card, customize your personal message, add photos and  click your</span><span> mouse. You never touch the card. TheCardMom.com will print, stuff,  stamp</span><span> and mail your cards. Try this amazing technology for free today and  I</span><span> promise you’ll be hooked. Go to </span><a href="http://www.thecardmom.com/"><span>www.thecardmom.com.</span></a>
