those techniques to help people lose weight. She doesn't care as much
about which diet you are using as long as you eat less calories she
cares more about how you are going about the weight loss process. It is
here where she is very helpful. Some of the weight loss tips she gave
our listeners were: pre-plan your eating each day; only eat sitting
down, remind yourself that hunger is never an emergency. She had many
more tips but you'll have to listen to the show with a pencil and paper
