			<title>Lisa Lillien The Hungry-Girl Recipes &amp; Guilt Free Eating Tips. Dr Scire's Brain Balance. Planet Smoothie &amp; The Daily Candy</title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://traffic.libsyn.com/weightlossradio/lose_weight_radio_podcast_06152008_64.MP3]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal">The most entertaining weight loss and fitness podcast show
on radio.&quot; Please click on the POD button to listen to the latest Dr. Fitness and the Fat Guy
