the Fat Guy</a> radio show podcast broadcasting live each week from Atlanta, GA, USA.&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=88916078">To download the show on iTunes please click on this link</a><br/><br/>Tonight we did the show without Dr Fitness who was partying on South Beach probably with Jennifer Nicole Lee and other hot models. But we had in his place the lovely Kathie Larkin and Tiffany Davis Atlanta Editor of the Daily Candy.<br/><br/>On
