<p>On tonight's show,&nbsp;Doctor Fitness and the Fat Guy get the skinny
about weight loss and fitness from Sgt Harvey Walden, star of the Celebrity Fit Club on <a href="http://www.vh1.com">VH1</a> and England's &quot;Fat Club&quot; Sgt Harvey has whipped celebrities like: Gary Busey, Tempestt Bledsoe, Kelly LeBrock, Tina Yothers and Vincent Pastore into shape on his popular fitness and weight loss TV show. He recently completed &quot;The Celebrity Fit Club Bootcamp Workout&quot; dvd and his book &quot;Harvey's No Excuses Workout&quot; will be out in August. Sgt Harvey believes in tough love and doesn't take kindly to excuses. So if you want some of his best tips and a little behind the scenes gossip from one of TV's best personal trainers you're going to love tonight's show.</p>

