...Dr Fitness' &quot;Things You Can Do Today&quot; To Lose Weight
Tomorrow.&nbsp;Here are
a&nbsp;few of Dr. Fitness' secrets about how to make sure you are doing a well balanced workout when you strength train...Number 1, always do a full body workout. Don't do arms one day and legs another day. Number 2, only do 8-12 exercises when you workout at the gym. And
Number
3, don't spend too much time on one body part, especially your core. Those one hour abs classes are a waste of time and you can get hurt. <br/><br/>Kathie was in Michigan doing something for the Real Savvy Moms TV show but she did give away some of our books which made the doctor happy. She'll be away for the next couple of weeks as she films
